{"_id":"YPvIBxQm10hZHG81","name":"Junction B-1","permission":{"default":0,"q8HmJQOf882klbgH":3},"folder":"tL9Z0ObBtwDIueRH","sort":300000,"flags":{},"content":"<p>The ladder is undamaged and all doors at this junction work.</p>"}
{"_id":"ZHb8VIAwra9h1JTx","name":"Vestibules","permission":{"default":0,"q8HmJQOf882klbgH":3},"folder":"tL9Z0ObBtwDIueRH","sort":400000,"flags":{},"content":"<p>Adjacent to Junction B-1 are two bays for class A individual escape pods embedded in the outer hull wall. All of the pods are missing (the only escape pod still remaining is in Clayton&rsquo;s corporate suite, below.)</p>\n<p>If the PCs are tense and power has yet to be restored, they might mistake the two bulky, empty, red-armored EVA suits (equivalent to @Item[wPYB3GmAoIBNBCiX]{Eco All Worlds Survival Suit}) standing in the shadows for lurking stalkers.</p>\n<p>Opening fire here is a bad idea, as it could compromise the hull.</p>"}
