{"_id":"09ytZihAXqm1AqOY","name":"Catwalk","permission":{"default":0,"q8HmJQOf882klbgH":3},"folder":"vLYOkqihUZdRuy61","sort":400001,"flags":{},"content":"<p>The catwalk overlooks the vehicle bay.</p>\n<p>A crane on ceiling tracks loads cargo to and from the vehicle bay and the cargo deck.</p>\n<p>Aside from directly in front of the cargo bay doors, the catwalk has a railing on either side, and the only way to reach the Technical section from this deck is to cross it.</p>"}
